# Named Entity Recognition with Keras

1. Prepare the dataset

Put dataset into `data` directory and the directory should contain three file.
```
/data
    test.txt
    train.txt
    valid.txt
```

2. Download the embedding

http://nlp.stanford.edu/projects/glove/

After you download the file, extract it into `embedding` directory.

3. Training

```
python train.py
```

